                              'Togglo' 1.01

                           by Charles-N. Jacob

  "Togglo" is a @{" Workbench game " link play} played on a 7 by 7 tiles board, in
which you have to 'toggle' or pivot tiles in such a way that they
make vertical or horizontal alignments of at least 2 neighbouring
tiles of the same colour... the more tiles there are, the more
points you make.

  Have fun!

